p; Technology), Aectiva (Aesthetic, Culture &amp; Conservation), dan Envisco (Environment, Sustainability &amp; Community). Fakultas Industri Kreatif memiliki 3 Center of Excellence (CoE) yaitu CoE Design Project &amp; Consultancy (HASTALOKA), CoE Digital Assset &amp; Craftsmanship (CIPTALOKA), dan CoE Professional Development &amp; Competencies (KARSALOKA). Selain itu, Fakultas Industri Kreatif juga memiliki prodi di kampus-kampus cabang, yaitu prodi DKV di Jakarta, prodi Desain Produk &amp; DKV di Purwokerto.', 'Ignored', '2026-01-23 00:35:34', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
